Feel: Medium bodied.  Crisp and soo refreshing!
Overall:  This is hands down the best pale ale that I have ever tasted.  Lives up to the hype in my opinion.  Alpha King not far behind though.  So far have had 4 different brews from these guys and all have been great.  Seems like these guys can't miss. 649 characterstrygelski1, Jan 10, 2016
