4.81/5  rDev +6.2%look: 4.5 | smell: 4.75 | taste: 5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.75I am a HUGE fan of Zombie Dust.  This rating is based on having it dozens of times (at the brewery, from the bottle, on tap) and every single time I am really impressed with it. 
