S: Amazing.  Grapefruit, jackfruit, a background of onions and garlic, a solid dankness.  Passion fruit, caramel, orange and orange peel.  Strong and in your face goodness upon opening.
T: Orange citrus, lemon candy, grapefruit pith, jackfruit, onions and garlic, passionfruit.  Good malt back bone, and good fresh Citra hops.  A solid bitterness on the end.  The oily resins from the hops coat your mouth and tongue, leaving them sticky like the tongue of a hummingbird in spring.
M:  Medium body, sticky hop coating on the tongue and teeth.  Medium low fine bubbled carbonation.
