Appearance: ZD poured a cloudy honey color with a finger thick marshmallow colored foam floating on top; ultimately this settled to a thin film on the surface.
Smell: Sweet clover honey, pineapple, tangerine & grapefruit, hoppy floral notes dance around the glass. I get some bready malt notes as well. Great smelling beer.
