Acquired in a trade with oldschool9
From 12 oz bottle to pint glass
A: Sticky copper glow emits from this delightfully lit brew with an off-white head that dissipates quickly into a familiar IPA appearance. Props to the label art. 
S: Luscious hops on the front combined with an incredibly pleasant malt sweetness. It's a honeycomb, sweet tea like aroma that is oh so pleasantly blended with the basket of citrus. 
